3 Group Assignment
In assigning groups, each team should have a leading sponsor of the project with
a preconcieved vision of how to move the relevant ways of working in a more
positive direction. They should also include the appropriate delegates from the
DevOps, Release Management and Test teams, as well as a D365 developer representative
to contribute views on how any changes would affect their everyday
work. Finally, two BAs will be required to translate takeaways from the sessions
into a proposed JIRA plan to accompany the final business case.
